    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Find the true cost of printing by calculating cost per page, cost per 100 pages, and monthly printing expenses.</p>

    <%# Ad: leaderboard — placed below content heading per AdSense best practices %>
